shadowsun-by-tonic (1.0+1-0ddebs4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * update to standards-version 4.6.0.1
  * make use of debhelper-compat (= 12) dependency, and remove
    debian/compat file
  * preferred to use pkgconf which requires less dependencies during
    build
  * added libgl-dev as a build dependency, to get -lGl for the linker,
    on jammy
  * replaced libsdl1.2 by libsdl1.2-compat to use SDL2 instead of SDL1.2

